HEADWORD: Pyxidium
<hw>Pyx*id"i*um</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>; <plu><it>pl.</it>
<plw>Pyxidia</plw> <pr>(#)</pr>.</plu> <ety>[NL., fr. Gr. <?/, dim. a
